title: Feeling Minnesota (1996)
description:
Feeling Minnesota
Year: 1996
Genre: Comedy
Starring: Keanu Reeves, Vincent DOnofrio, Cameron Diaz, Delroy Lindo, Courtney Love,
Director: Steven Baigelman

Synopsis
Chaos, violence, and a Cain-and-Abel-like struggle ensue when, on the day of her wedding, a young midwesterner makes the mistake of falling in love with another man -her fiances brother. An independent romantic comedy.
